---
title: Salmon with Maple Dijon Sauce plus Sweet Potato, Zucchini & Red Onion Jumble
description: Looking to spice things up with a new sauce? A mix of sweet maple syrup and tangy Dijon mustard make a deliciously balanced finishing drizzle for juicy seared chicken cutlets. While we’re playing matchmaker, you’ll serve the chicken atop a sweet, earthy jumble of sautéed sweet potatoes, zucchini, and red onion, all in a speedy 20 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66156a1811089628acd331c3-2fec14db.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66d8bfda84d92a4240f34eff-en-US.pdf
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 610 kcal
  fat: 37 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 36 g
  sugar: 18 g
  protein: 33 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 1100 mg
